   "source": [
    "# T09 GARCH -- A股波动率建模与预测\n",
    "\n",
    "## 0. 论文信息\n",
    "\n",
    "| 字段 | 内容 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| **参考** | Bollerslev(1986) JoE; 方意&荣雪(2019)《管理世界》35(7) |\n",
    "| **核心问题** | A股收益率存在ARCH效应吗？GARCH(1,1)能准确刻画波动率聚集？ |\n",
    "| **方法** | GARCH(p,q)，MLE估计条件方差，含持续性检验与波动率预测 |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "edee2ae1",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 研究设计\n",
    "\n",
    "**波动率聚集**: 大波动后跟大波动，方差时变，OLS同方差假设不成立。\n",
    "\n",
    "**ARCH-LM检验**: 对残差平方做辅助回归，$H_0$：无ARCH效应（$LM = nR^2 \\sim \\chi^2_q$）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "31a2ffd4",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 数学理论\n",
    "\n",
    "**GARCH(p,q) 方差方程**:\n",
    "$$\\sigma_t^2 = \\omega + \\sum_{i=1}^q \\alpha_i \\varepsilon_{t-i}^2 + \\sum_{j=1}^p \\beta_j \\sigma_{t-j}^2$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**约束**: $\\omega>0,\\ \\alpha_i\\geq0,\\ \\beta_j\\geq0,\\ \\sum\\alpha_i+\\sum\\beta_j<1$\n",
    "\n",
    "**持续性**: $\\text{Persistence} = \\sum\\alpha_i + \\sum\\beta_j$ (接近1表示冲击持久)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "482177c4",
   "metadata": {},
